main event: Four black objects the size of a pencil eraser were observed flying in a cluster in Travis County, Texas, on April 30, 1955.
interesting points: The objects traveled from west to east,The sighting lasted for about 2-3 seconds,A 'whooshing' sound was heard during the sighting,The report classified the objects as unidentified,The source of the report was military.
sighted object: four black objects in the sky
